{"tid":1032740,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 不願面對亦需承認：ARM 版 Mac 電腦最快 2020 年殺到！","createTime":"2019-02-22T15:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T17:27:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7cce96c538d613c9424cfb42489a5943da20ad97","tid":1032740,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"隨住 Apple 自家研發的 A 系列處理器越來越強大，近年不時傳出 Apple 將會在自己的 Mac 系列產品中，放棄自 PowerPC 末落以來一直延用至今的 Intel 處理器，從而換上自家的 A 系列處理器。這個舉動其實已經越來越明顯，如實行的話表示 Intel 繼失去行動裝置市場後，連桌面電腦的 Mac 這個「鐵客」亦可能失去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/2019/02/22/arm-macs-could-come-as-soon-as-2020/macbook-future-fb/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F02%2F22%2Farm-macs-could-come-as-soon-as-2020%2Fmacbook-future-fb%2F&h=4facde1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據 Appleinsider 引述 Axios 消息報導，Intel 日前已經正式地表示，Apple 將改用自家 ARM 架構的 A 系列處理器最快將會在 2020 年實行。這說明了，Apple 現時或已經減少甚至中止了向 Intel 採購處理器的合約，繼而推出 ARM 架構的 Mac 系列電腦。<br />\n<br />\n現時無論是 Windows 的 PC 或 Apple 的 Mac 系列桌面電腦，都是採用 X86 架構，因此基本上只會採用 Intel 或 AMD 的處理器。而現時行動裝置，包括智能手機、平板電腦等，均屬 ARM 架構。因此，由 X86 轉至 ARM，最大的阻礙便是軟件的執行。不過，無論是 Windows 或 macOS，均已經在探討 ARM 架構的兼容。<br />\n<br />\n現時 Windows 已經有 ARM 版本，在行動裝置界處理器霸王的 Qualcomm 亦推出了 Snapdragon 850 處理器以供 Windows 10 電腦使用。至於 Apple，由日前的 Project Marzipan 已經可以得知，不需要那麼麻煩，因為日後 iOS 平台 App 可以更快移植到 Mac 裝置上使用，令到 Mac 系列電腦在架構轉換時可以更平穩快速地轉換。"},{"pid":"52dac314c31a486905c69ab5d39191dd4429d63e","tid":1032740,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/02/22/arm-macs-could-come-as-soon-as-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F02%2F22%2Farm-macs-could-come-as-soon-as-2020%2F&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=6c33a234\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/02/22/arm-macs-could-come-as-soon-as-2020/</a>"},{"pid":"282ff4b759d11697c74c99f477a570e067cbc380","tid":1032740,"uid":15564,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"Apple不願面對亦須承認：4g依賴intel"},{"pid":"942b12278c7411dc7b7a24ae546bb1cd7b059c0b","tid":1032740,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84bf2199319147febd85245b2900422d486a78d9","tid":1032740,"uid":188176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T15:52:13.000Z","msg":"2019咁快有笑話"},{"pid":"e1da781eae54f289c8c52d7b204d1b4a64d09269","tid":1032740,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T23:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3702cf35b5f3134b07da86d0193479eb9dbf1308","tid":1032740,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:00:24.000Z","msg":"如果係咁 ipad用到mac啲軟件就無敵"},{"pid":"8768e14dc9ec014639e565ed010829d8462b813c","tid":1032740,"uid":53466,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:05:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d145756d4260d514633e6790254afa07d2eaf1ea","tid":1032740,"uid":22553,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:23:14.000Z","msg":"文書機arm已夠做，得繪圖/剪影片嗰啲要大量運算仲係x86天下"},{"pid":"f0124e2a2569b76f70c5f6ef99595b41bd87ff9d","tid":1032740,"uid":193131,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後仲有冇咁多人買macbook，好多人買返黎都係bootcamp裝windows<br />\n短時間內應該冇咁快有ARM版的bootcamp"},{"pid":"4b2073b60c09d99194e05b9441cd82ea0e219402","tid":1032740,"uid":815,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f0124e2a2569b76f70c5f6ef99595b41bd87ff9d","tid":1032740,"uid":193131,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T00:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後仲有冇咁多人買macbook，好多人買返黎都係bootcamp裝windows<br />\n短時間內應該